Text: With greater clarity to the opportunities ahead, we're confidently updating our five-year strategic growth plan and financial outlook. VF expects 12 to 14 percent rise in EPS by 2024 Gross margin is expected to exceed 55.5 percent in fiscal 2024, while operating margin is expected to exceed 15 percent. The company added that earnings per share (EPS) are expected to grow at a five-year CAGR of between 12 percent and 14 percent as compared to fiscal 2019 adjusted EPS.
